node.text: #TSRTPositiveImages: @FashionNovaCares and #TheShadeRoom @NoIGAngelica donate $100K to @Peace4Kids to support their ROCMove initiative. @ROCMove is a multigenerational initiative led predominantly by women and girls with lived experience in foster care. It's designed to uplift media and interactive training to highlight stories of power, transformation and resilience, evolving our country’s negative perception of foster care. For 22 years Peace4Kids has been fueled by the idea that youth in foster care deserve equitable opportunities to create community and connect with people who authentically care for them. Peace4Kids honors the intergenerational voices of foster care and provides the tools to navigate past trauma, embrace the future and thrive.  #NationalFosterCareMonth #FashionNovaCares

node.title: Fashion Nova & TSR Donate to Peace4Kids

node.text:
#StaceyAbrams stepped in to discuss the importance of young black people voting in this election! “People tend to vote more when they get what they want— that’s why seniors vote so much.” 

Well TeaMates, young people outnumber the old heads so we could get what WE want if we cast our ballots. We’re powerful in numbers, and that’s why people try to stop us from showing up to the polls. Visit iWillVote.com for more info. 

Drop a ✊🏾 if you’re down to vote or already have!

#AsianDoll was not feeling the fact that The #TaylorGirlz dropped a YouTube video in response to her audio.

She says she didn’t care if she was being recorded or not & stand 10 toes behind everything that was said said. 
___________________________

node.text: #TSRTFamilyAffairz: Yasss! #SmoothGio moved his parents out of an apartment into a brand new house 🙌🏾 #WeLoveToSeeIt

The #TaylorGirlz respond to #AsianDoll’s claims that Ti was trying to take over her studio session with #Future & not wanting her on the ‘Bundles’ remix. 
___________________________
#TiTaylor says the studio session happened August 23rd & after she was still hanging out with Asian so she doesn’t understand why their is ‘beef’ now.

They said that multiple artist were invited to studio session & it everyone was allowed to play their music. 
_________________________
#DayshaTaylor also dropped a few clip receipts in response to Asian’s leaked audio. 
_________________________
Ti also says she had not control over Asian being featured on the #KaylaNicole’s Bundles remix! ( SWIPE )

node.text: #TSRTIssaLinkUp: #ClarenceNYC, #KenWalker, & #ModDaGod was real litt last night! 🍻

#TeaMates, today makes 25 yearssss  since #BluesClues aired on TV. Throughout the years this show has definitely touched many generations. 
__________________________
#SteveBurns even tugged on a few of our hearts a lil as he gave many closure since he left for college 💙 
__________________________
Since the air date a lot of changes have a made, new characters have joined, but the memories are forver locked into our childhoods ! SWIPE & drop your favorite moments/charters 🐾 🍿 ( 🎥: @nickjr )
